[[Munatsi]] (Refiner in English) zvinoreva nzvimbo inoitwa mabasa ekuchenesa simbi kuchibviswa [[manyara]] asingadiwe musimbi iyi. Simbi dzinonatswa nenzira dzakasiyana dzinosanganisira: kunyautsa nemoto; kunyunguditsa nekupatsanura zvine [[huduma]] hwakasiyana; kuchenesa nenzira dzinotsauranisa nemagetsi.


MuZimbabwe tine Vanatsi vesimbi vanoti: Bindura Smelter and Refinery; Empress Nickel Refinery; Zimasco neZimAlloys.


